target: You're welcome. Have a great stay!
context: <user> I am looking for a train arriving by 9:45 on Tuesday. <system> May I get your departure and destination information please? <user> I am going from Cambridge to Leicester. <system> TR2863 departs from Cambridge at 07:21 and arrive in Leicester by 09:06. Would you like to book this train? <user> Maybe... how much does it cost? <system> It costs 37.80 pounds per ticket. <user> I'm sorry, we have that mixed up. I need to depart from leicester and go to cambridge. Do you have a train that arrives by 09:45 in cambridge? <system> TR6954 departs from Leicester at 07:09 and arrives in Cambridge at 08:54. Would you like to book this train?<user> Can you verify the cost for train TR6954 for me? <system> The cost for this particular train is 37.80 pounds per ticket. Would you like assistance booking tickets for this train?<user> Yes I would like help with booking the train and I will also need to book a hotel. <system> Your booking reference is NT43PSC0 . Now, if you let me know what type of hotel you are interested in, I can help you with that as well.<user> Can you help me find a 5-star room somewhere that offers free parking and wifi? <system> There don't seem to be any 5-star lodgings in the city. Would you like to try searching for 4 stars instead?<user> Yes, 4 stars would be fine. <system> The acorn guest house is a 4 star hotel located in the north side. Would you like to make reservations?<user> Yes please. There are 5 of us total and we need 4 nights in a row. Thank you. <system> What day would like to start your stay?<user> I'd like to start my stay on Tuesday, please. <system> Ok great! I was able to get you booked, your reference number is N4TJE8VR . Is there anything else that I can help you with?<user> Nope, that'll take care of everything, thanks! <system>
